OL,5,G2100 Bill Bailey's Vietnam
OL,6,     FIn Ho Chi Minh City, the most
OL,7,     Fpopulous city in Vietnam, Bill is
OL,8,     Fcaught between wartime tunnels,
OL,9,     Fendless crazy traffic, and a deep
OL,10,     Fdive into a local musical twist of
OL,11,     Fmetal versus folk. (Ep2)
OL,12,G2200 Bill Bailey: Larks in Transit
OL,13,     FBill becomes the first British
OL,14,     Fcomedian to tread the boards of
OL,15,     Fthe Royal Opera House as he goes
OL,16,     Fdown the rabbit hole with Google
OL,17,     Freviews of Poundland, and Samuel
